{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/132/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/132.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/132/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/132/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/132/joint-command-message-not-interpreted"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/132/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Maurice Fallon", "uuid": "{8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/abb08cebf2b2b2fb3ae3f65fde4d36c0d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsMF-4.png"}}, "nickname": "mauricefallon", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:82a58458-5b27-457e-8e75-da6e16d4e3df"}, "title": "joint command message not interpreted properly", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 2, "content": {"raw": "Currently in both the sandia and atlas plugins the joint ordering is hardcoded.\r\n\r\nThe joint command message has a 'name' array field. This ordering is not used by the plugins - so if joint angles aren't published in the ordering specified in the cpp of the plugins they aren't interpreted properly.\r\n\r\nthe plugins should be reading this order from the message and using a map.\r\n\r\nThis is a major bug and can be easily fixed.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Currently in both the sandia and atlas plugins the joint ordering is hardcoded.</p>\n<p>The joint command message has a 'name' array field. This ordering is not used by the plugins - so if joint angles aren't published in the ordering specified in the cpp of the plugins they aren't interpreted properly.</p>\n<p>the plugins should be reading this order from the message and using a map.</p>\n<p>This is a major bug and can be easily fixed.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "state": "resolved", "version": {"name": "2.1.0", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/versions/49845.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-02-15T19:06:48.477554+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-04-11T02:58:42.875355+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 132}